ResourceHeader.ResourceName: ACE Solar Isotope Spectrometer (SIS) 1-Hour Level 2 Data
ResourceHeader.Description: ACE SIS Solar Isotopic Spectrometer (SIS) intensities and counts, for 8 elements at 1-hour time resolution. Calibrated science quality data.
